Mzamo Xala, newly appointed group CEO; Zibusiso Mkhwanazi, cofounder and Veli Ngubane, co-founding partner of Avatar AgencyWith its roots firmly on the ground, Avatar has it eyes set on the next 10 years. The agency group hopes to cement its approach and continue to inspire, integrate, and innovate ideas that move people. Veli Ngubane, Avatar’s co-founding partner, will continue to enrich the groups creative pedigree as chief creative officer, working closely alongside Xala.We will continue to showcase and demonstrate how our world-class people, working with world-class clients, come together to create world-class work. “The encouragement, challenges and feedback our clients’ give us to inspire us to do better, every day. We will continue to challenge ourselves to deliver work that is relevant, original and impactful,” adds Xala.“In the next 10 years, we will keep raising the bar. We can’t thank our teams, partners, and Clients enough for all their contributions to the growth of Avatar. We will be celebrating this milestone throughout 2022 and we look forward to having them alongside us as we shape the future of marketing, media and advertising together in the next decade,” ends Mkhwanazi.